        public com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.Model loadModel(String filenameOrURI)
        Loads RDF model from URI. If URI is prefix-mapped, local file is returned. If the URI is SPARQL Protocol URI (contains endpoint and encoded query), the query is decoded and executed on the endpoint. Otherwise, attempting to reading RDF from Linked Data URI.
        Overrides:
